}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b\f1 67-69.}{\plain \fs24 \f1   The father's premature lament for his living son (but he }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 will}{\plain \fs24 \f1  be dead in four \softline
